+
+  <description>
+    This IT tests what happens if the method name in a single class BeanA gets changed.
+    In this case 'mvn compile' (without a clean) should fail as  BeanA2
+    still uses the old method of BeanA.
+  </description>
+
+  <build>
+    <pluginManagement>
+      <plugins>
+        <plugin>
